🌐 Deployment on Vercel
Push your code to a GitHub repository.

Import the project into Vercel.

Add the environment variables (VITE_SUPABASE_URL, VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY) in the Vercel dashboard.

Deploy – your app will be live at a *.vercel.app URL.

